\c 11
\s USawuli unqoba amaAmoni
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusenyuka uNahashi umAmoni\x + 12.12. 14.47. Gen. 19.38. Dute. 2.19.23.3. Hlu. 3.13. 10.7,11. 11.4,15,33. 2 Sam. 10.1. 1 Kho. 11.1,5,7,33.\x*, wamisa inkamba maqondana leJabeshi-Gileyadi\x + Hlu. 21.8.\x*; wonke amadoda eJabeshi asesithi kuNahashi: Yenza isivumelwano lathi, sizakusebenzela\x + Gen. 26.28. Eks. 23.22. 34.12,15. Dute. 7.2. 1 Kho. 20.34. Jobe 41.4. Hez. 17.13.\x*.
\v 2 Kodwa uNahashi umAmoni wathi kibo: Ngizasenza phezu kwalokhu \add isivumelwano\add* lani\x + 1 Kho. 8.9.\x*, ukuze ngilikopole wonke amehlo awesokunene\x + Nani 16.14.\x* njalo ngehlisele uIsrayeli wonke ihlazo\x + 17.26. Gen. 34.14.\x*.
\v 3 Abadala beJabeshi basebesithi kuye: Siyekele okwensuku eziyisikhombisa ukuze sithume izithunywa kuwo wonke umngcele wakoIsrayeli. Uba-ke kungekho ongasisindisa, sizaphuma size kuwe.
\p
\v 4 Izithunywa zasezifika eGibeya kaSawuli\x + 10.26. Josh. 18.28.\x*, zalandisa amazwi endlebeni zabantu, labantu bonke baphakamisa ilizwi labo bakhala inyembezi\x + Hlu. 2.4. 21.2.\x*.
\v 5 Khangela-ke, uSawuli weza emva kwezinkabi evela emasimini, uSawuli wathi: \add Kwenze\add* njani ebantwini ukuthi bakhale? Basebemtshela amazwi amadoda eJabeshi.
\v 6 UMoya kaNkulunkulu wasefika ngamandla phezu kukaSawuli lapho esizwa lawomazwi, lolaka lwakhe lwavutha kakhulu\x + 10.6,10. Hlu. 3.10.\x*.
\v 7 Wasethatha inkabi ezimbili, waziquma zaba yiziqa, wazithumela kuwo wonke umngcele wakoIsrayeli ngesandla sezithunywa esithi\x + Hlu. 19.29. 1 Kho. 18.23,33.\x*: Ongaphumi alandele uSawuli alandele loSamuweli, kuzakwenziwanje enkabini zakhe. Ukwesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* kwasekusehlela phezu kwabantu, baphuma njengamuntu munye\x + Hlu. 21.5,8,10.\x*.
\v 8 Lapho ebabala eBezeki\x + Hlu. 1.5.\x*, abantwana bakoIsrayeli babe yizinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amathathu, lamadoda akoJuda eyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu\x + Hlu. 20.15-17. 2 Sam. 24.9.\x*.
\v 9 Basebesithi kuzo izithunywa ezazifikile: Lizawatshela njalo amadoda eJabeshi-Gileyadi \add lithi\add*: Kusasa lizakuba losindiso nxa ilanga selitshisa. Lapho izithunywa zifika zawatshela amadoda eJabeshi, athokoza.
\v 10 Ngakho amadoda eJabeshi athi: Kusasa sizaphumela kini, lenze kithi njengakho konke okulungileyo emehlweni enu\x + 11.3.\x*.
\v 11 Kwasekusithi kusisa, uSawuli\x + 31.11.\x* wamisa abantu ngezigaba ezintathu\x + Hlu. 7.16.\x*; bafika phakathi kwenkamba ngomlindo wekuseni\x + Eks. 14.24.\x*; bamtshaya uAmoni lwaze lwatshisa usuku; kwasekusithi abaseleyo bahlakazeka, kwaze kwathi kakusalanga kibo ababili bendawonye.
\p
\v 12 Abantu basebesithi kuSamuweli: Ngubani othe: USawuli uzabusa yini phezu kwethu\x + 10.27.\x*? Baletheni labobantu ukuze sibabulale\x + Luka 19.27.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa uSawuli wathi: Kakuyikubulawa muntu ngalolusuku\x + 2 Sam. 19.22.\x*, ngoba lamuhla iN\nd kosi\nd* yenze inkululeko koIsrayeli\x + 19.5. Eks. 14.13.\x*.
\v 14 USamuweli wasesithi ebantwini: Wozani siye eGiligali\x + 10.8.\x*, sivuselele umbuso khona.
\v 15 Bonke abantu basebesiya eGiligali, bambeka khona uSawuli waba yinkosi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* eGiligali\x + 10.17. Hlu. 11.11.\x*. Bahlaba khona imihlatshelo yeminikelo yokuthula phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, lalapho uSawuli lawo wonke amadoda akoIsrayeli bathokoza kakhulukazi\x + 10.8.\x*.